# 全域配置引用修復計畫 (第二輪)

本計畫旨在徹底解決 [AppConfig](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Config/AppConfig.cs#19-120) 模組化重構後，剩餘檔案中未更新的屬性引用問題。

## 待遷移引用清單

| 舊屬性名 | 新路徑 |
| :--- | :--- |
| `BloodBarDetectIntervalMs` | `Vision.BloodBarDetectIntervalMs` |
| `MonsterDetectIntervalMs` | `Vision.MonsterDetectIntervalMs` |
| [DetectionMode](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Config/VisionSettings.cs#59-64) | `Vision.DetectionMode` |
| `DefaultThreshold` | `Vision.DefaultThreshold` |
| `MaxDetectionResults` | `Vision.MaxDetectionResults` |
| `CaptureFrameRate` | `Vision.CaptureFrameRate` |
| `GlobalArrivalTolerance` | `Navigation.ArrivalTolerance` |
| `LastSelectedWindowName` | `General.LastSelectedWindowName` |
| [MinimapViewer](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MinimapViewer.cs#41-67) | `Appearance.MinimapViewer` |
| `PartyRedBar` | `Appearance.PartyRedBar` |
| `DetectionBox` | `Appearance.DetectionBox` |
| `AttackRange` | `Appearance.AttackRange` |
| [Minimap](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Models/Minimap/MinimapStyles.cs#7-27) | `Appearance.Minimap` |
| [Monster](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/GameVisionCore.cs#449-573) | `Appearance.Monster` |
| [MinimapPlayer](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Models/Minimap/MinimapStyles.cs#32-64) | `Appearance.MinimapPlayer` |

